insighttoolkit4 (4.3.2-1ubuntu2) saucy; urgency=low

  * debian/patches/bool-is-not-bool.patch: make sure our C bool type matches
    the C++ bool type.  Fixes a bug found by the test suite, caused by trying
    to pass a pointer to a C++ native 'bool' as a pointer to a C 'int' bool.
  * debian/patches/add-missing-include.patch: add a missing include of
    itkProgressReporter.h.
